<li><a href="../tag/t1c.html"><span class="tagM">T1C: Behavioural Semantics</span></a><ul><li> The paper primarily develops behavioural/executable semantics or ways to execute semantic definitions.
</li></ul></li>
<li><a href="../tag/t4a.html"><span class="tagL">T4A: Workbenches</span></a><ul><li> It includes substantial tool support or infrastructure relevant for engineering/using languages.
</li></ul></li>
